title: DOOM Eternal with Elyse Willems
description: Elyse Willems (Funhaus) joins The Besties for an in-depth conversation on the newly released Doom Eternal! Topics include ripping of arms and limbs, the world-building of hell on earth and space castles.
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (The Besties)
